---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout title="About — Safraz Razik">
  <section class="container-main section-padding">
    <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl">
      <p class="section-label">About</p>
      <h1 class="text-3xl font-bold text-gray-900 sm:text-4xl">About Me</h1>
      <div class="mt-8 space-y-5 text-base leading-relaxed text-gray-600">
        <p>
          I'm <strong class="text-gray-900">Safraz Razik</strong> — founder of <strong class="text-gray-900">Zetmel</strong>, an AI-accelerated software engineering studio.
        </p>
        <p>
          I'm a software professional with 15+ years in full-stack development, project leadership, and startup co-founding. My expertise spans modern JavaScript frameworks (React, Vue, TypeScript, Next.js), backend systems (Node.js, PHP, Python), and enterprise platforms like Oracle Commerce Cloud and Oracle Storefront Framework.
        </p>
        <p>
          What sets my work apart today is the integration of AI into the engineering process. I run local LLM environments (Ollama, OpenCode, Claude Code), evaluate coding models (Qwen, Llama, DeepSeek) for code quality and task fit, and use structured prompting and context-management workflows to coordinate multi-stage development — all while maintaining production standards through technical audits and recovery sprints.
        </p>
        <p>
          I've delivered solutions at Fortune 500 companies (Motorola Solutions) and startups alike, co-founded ventures, built open-source tools (<a href="https://github.com/safrazik/vue-file-agent">Vue File Agent</a>, <a href="https://github.com/rockplate/rockplate">Rockplate</a>), and contributed to projects across web, mobile, and desktop platforms.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mt-10">
        <a href="/resume/" class="btn-primary">
          View full resume
          <i class="ri-arrow-right-line"></i>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
